      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ…はぁ…",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 69.4753060499827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 69.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "（当然よ）\n（私はここの誰よりも歌もダンスも努力してきた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Of course.)\n(I've worked harder on my singing and dancing than anyone else here…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7,
      "endTime": 75.27712011337277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "（あの話、きっとモノにしてみせる……！）\n（いえ、もう私に決まってるわ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I'll definitely make that rumor a reality…!)\n(No‚ it's already decided! It's going to be me!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.46666666666667,
      "endTime": 81.80344654719036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 82
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――莉央はアイドル候補生達の中で異彩を放っており",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio stood out among the idol trainees‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82,
      "endTime": 85.64,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "入所三ヶ月にして頭一つ抜けた存在になっていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and just three months after joining‚ she had become a cut above the rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.63333333333334,
      "endTime": 88.99333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ…はぁ…",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2,
      "endTime": 91.14024949073792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――デビューまであと一歩",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Just one step away from debut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.33333333333333,
      "endTime": 93.29333324432372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "養成所の誰もがそう感じていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone in the training center felt it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3,
      "endTime": 95.53999989827474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 95.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "――！\nはぁ、はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――!\nPant Pant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.73333333333333,
      "endTime": 99.78662136395775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央、お疲れ\n頑張っているな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ good work.\nYou're working hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100,
      "endTime": 103.69154195785521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 103.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
